data.description: The attached Townhouse was built in 1945 and offers 3 BR 1 Full Bath over a foyer, spacious LR and FDR, and a recently updated kitchen with Quartz countertops and stainless appliances including a dishwasher, and a gas stove. A fully finished basement with a private entrance full bath and large open room. Hardwood floors, recently replaced windows (main level, and 2nd floor) plus recently replaced front & back doors. A recently updated roof and solar panels. White PVC fenced front and back yard plus a 2-car detached garage. Citywide High School Choice. Buyers can assume the seller's VA Mortgage of $406,000 at a fixed rate of 2.7% for a 30-year term if they are a Veteran.
